name: Cathy
dialogue: Oh my god, have you guys seen the latest meme going around? It's literally the funniest thing ever! *giggles*

name: Eva
dialogue: Oh, do tell! I love memes! *smiling*

name: Cathy
dialogue: Well, it's this one where a cat is riding a Roomba and it's just so... *chuckles* I can't even handle it! Have you seen it?

name: Eva
dialogue: No, I haven't, but I can't wait to see it! *excitedly* Where did you see it?

name: Cathy
dialogue: Oh, it was on Twitter. I saw it and just died laughing! *giggles* It's just so... *chuckles* I can't even explain it.

name: Eva
dialogue: Well, I'm glad you're enjoying it! Humor is always the best way to lift someone's spirits. *smiling*

name: Cathy
dialogue: Totally! And speaking of humor, have you heard about that new comedy show that's coming out? It looks hilarious! *giggles* I can't wait to watch it!

name: Eva
dialogue: Oh, really? Which one is it? *curious*

name: Cathy
dialogue: It's called "The Laughter League" and it looks so... *chuckles* I just can't wait to see it! *giggles* Have you heard anything about it?

name: Eva
dialogue: Yes, I have! I heard it's going to be a real riot! *smiling* I can't wait to watch it either! *excitedly*
